YATRI_POINTS_FAQS_QUES1_ANS2 _: The earned Yatri Points make you eligible for discount points, which can be used on the platform.
YATRI_POINTS_FAQS_QUES1_ANS3 _: Each Yatri point can be converted to 0.1 discount point, which will be adjusted against the subscription fee as per the plan.
YATRI_POINTS_FAQS_QUES1_ANS4 _: Please refer to the usage section in terms and conditions for more information -
YATRI_POINTS_FAQS_QUES2 _: What is the validity of Yatri Points?

YATRI_POINTS_FAQS_QUES3 _: How can I earn Yatri Points?

YATRI_POINTS_FAQS_QUES3_ANS2 _: You can earn additional points by exhibiting good behavior, such as low cancellations and receiving good ratings from customers.
YATRI_POINTS_FAQS_QUES4 _: How can I use the Yatri Points I earned?
YATRI_POINTS_FAQS_QUES4_ANS1 _: Yatri Points earned will be converted into Discount Points as per Namma Yatri's policy.
YATRI_POINTS_FAQS_QUES4_ANS2 _: To be eligible for Discount Points, a minimum Yatri Points must be earned.
YATRI_POINTS_FAQS_QUES4_ANS3 _: Discount Points will be adjusted against the subscription fee as per the plan.
YATRI_POINTS_FAQS_QUES5 _: What is the eligibility to earn and use Yatri Points?
YATRI_POINTS_FAQS_QUES5_ANS1 _: You must complete your first ride with Namma Yatri to start earning Yatri Points.
YATRI_POINTS_FAQS_QUES5_ANS2 _: The Yatri Points section will be disabled until you complete your first ride.
